headline: Lamar's Q4 AFFO Beats Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: LAMR tops Q4 AFFO estimates as revenues rise 2.8% Y/Y and local and national sales improve. It issues 2026 AFFO guidance.

headline: Assessing Prologis (PLD) Valuation After Dividend Hike And Data Center Co Investment Fund Plans
summary: Dividend increase and data center plans put Prologis in focus Prologis (PLD) has moved into the spotlight after raising its annualized dividend by 6% to $4.28 per share and outlining plans for a data center focused co investment fund and new development projects.
